# ABU Pick4Me 🍽️

**Helping Ahmadu Bello University students cure decision paralysis, one meal at a time.**

## What It Does
ABU Pick4Me is a WhatsApp-powered food recommendation bot for ABU students. 
Students tell Chef Francois their budget, mood, and location — he finds the best 
verified food vendors instantly and delivers recommendations straight to WhatsApp.

## How It Works
1. Student messages Chef Francois on WhatsApp
2. Bot collects: Name → Campus → Budget → Craving
3. Bot scans verified vendors near campus
4. Student gets personalized recommendations + earns ABU Coins
5. Coins redeemable for free drinks, discounts, and meals

## Tech Stack
- **Frontend:** HTML/CSS/JS landing page (GitHub Pages)
- **Backend:** Make.com automation platform
- **Messaging:** UltraMsg WhatsApp Business API
- **Data:** Google Sheets + Make.com Data Store

## Live Demo
🔗 https://haddir.github.io/ABU-PICK-4-ME/

## Features
- ✅ Personalized food picks based on budget & location
- ✅ ABU Coin loyalty system (earn while you eat)
- ✅ Referral rewards (+20 coins per friend)
- ✅ No app download needed — works in WhatsApp
- ✅ Built for ABU Samaru, Congo, Site II & off-campus

## Built For
Ahmadu Bello University Students, Zaria, Nigeria

